  // About
  section#about.about-section.text-center
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-8.mx-auto
          h2.mb-4 About us
          p
            span MusicSOL&nbsp;
          p
            | (pronounced myo&#x35E;oziks&omacr;l, SOL being the 5th solfege scale degree, similar sound to soul.)
          p
            | MusicSOL, LLC. is one of the world&rsquo;s premiere online music lessons school. 
            | Our unique learning environment engages our students and encourages them to take their education past the classroom, 
            | through world-class education and performances. 
            | MusicSOL students study with our distinguished faculty from over 20 countries and nearly every state. 
            | MusicSOL teachers are active members of their music communities and have occupied a unique place in music education. 
            | Our talented list of instructors come from Italy, Spain, Israel, Greece, England, Mexico, Canada, United States and more!
          p
            span
              | MusicSOL is an online music learning program for all ages. 
              | Our students not only receive lessons on their instrument/s of choice, 
              | but also receive dedicated instructions in music theory.
          p
            span
              | The instructors in our network create their own unique lesson plans based on what is best suited for each individual student.
          p
            span Sign up today to have our knowledgeable staff assist you.&nbsp;
          p
            span
              | COVID19 precautions: Learn in the comfort and safety of your own home. All lessons currently take place online. We have no binding contracts. We want you to always enjoy the lessons with your teacher. If something changes, you are free to cancel or change teachers at any time.
          p
            span Start your musical journey today!
